Jeremiah Ogbodo (a mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị nke 4 n'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 1991), nke a maara nke ọma dị ka Swanky Jerry, bụ onye ama ama na-emepụta ejiji ejiji na Naijiria nke a maara maka ọrụ ya na Tonto Dikeh, D'banj, Ice Prince, M.I, Tu Face, Juliet Ibrahim na Davido, tinyere ndị ọzọ.

Ogbodo malitere ọrụ ya dị ka onye ama ama na ejiji ejiji site na mmalite nke akara ya Swanky Signatures Styling na June 2012. Ewezuga ejiji ndị ahịa maka ngosipụta red carpet na ihe nkiri vidio, mkpuchi nke ọrụ ya apụtawo n'ọtụtụ magazin na akwụkwọ ntanetị
Ọ kpọrọ Darey maka House of Maliq, D'banj maka foto, Praiz, na Davido maka "All of You" mmepụta vidiyo egwu, n'etiti ndị ọzọ.
N'afọ 2014, Ogbodo meriri Fashion Stylist of the Year na Ihe Nrite Ejiji Lagos.
